{
  "stem": "2097.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I haven't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the-- the newspapers, and the people, they were whispering that what happening around the Europe-- especially I was in the school in 1938, I guess, it was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A family came to the relatives.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And their daughter-- I remember the family name was Fogel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They walked from Poland on foot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the gentleman was a very gigantic man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the girl, also was too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she was put in our-- in my class.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were there, briefly, in-- in the city, because they emigrated to Palestine, somehow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there he-- this man was telling to the local Jewish people, stories-- what happened in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They burned cities and towns, and all kinds of miseries.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans occupied Poland, at the time, already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe I mix them up, the years, because--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--'38 And '39 were so close, and so washed in my mind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so many other things happened, that I could mix it up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I definitely-- I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when this man was talking about what happened in Poland, and he was walking for three, four weeks from Poland to Simleu, nobody believed him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was thinking that he's crazy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So finally-- when he left-- and his family-- to Palestine, everybody was relieved.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody believed him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And instead of the Jewish community listen to him, and organize, they could've saved a lot of Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But nobody believed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the war was in Africa already, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother was reading the newspaper, and my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were talking, and we had no-- no life, the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody-- we didn't-- we weren't children, anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were just young adults, I should say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were just, we couldn't even smile.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
